channel.title: Made from ddsspec V2 client webclient
channel.description:
[size=15pt][b]IF YOU GOT A BRAIN YOU CAN EASY EDIT ALL CUSTOMS AND MODELS ECT.. DON'T COMPLAIN FOR THAT.[/b][/size]
I made this because I saw lots or people had problems with it. It loads currctly. All interface models, customs and all are loading. You just have to change:
[code]C:/.jvmtestwebclient_file_store_32/[/code] TO [code]C:/.YOURNAME_file_store_32/[/code]
And change my cache download to your cache download.
In ALL the files I did it. Just search it.
This is what I did. First the ip loaded from the gui, I chnaged the ip just loaded form the main class in client class. With the setserver methode.
The cache.zip is in the client folder to. Just extract and rezip it if you need to change.
Download: http://www.filefront.com/14011261/Ddsspeced%20V2%20Client.rar
[b][i][u]If you think i'm adverting I will remove!![/u][/i][/b]
Here is a pic it works correctly: [img]http://i30.tinypic.com/rbd6ie.jpg[/img]
For more info check Ric's his TUT: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,336494.0.html
